description: This common Gatinho purrs with a rating of 5, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 15, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Stringalong for East, Nine Lives for South, and Box for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [15 Votes, Common]
